{"article_id":"XFGKEbrn5DXjtcB1","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Donald Trump Jr was informed in an email ahead of a meeting with a Russian lawyer","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"that damaging information about Hillary Clinton","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"to be handed over","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"was part of an effort by the Russian government","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"to help the Trump campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"the New York Times has reported .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Rob Goldstone :","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"who is the man","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"who set up Trump Jr 's meeting with a Russian lawyer ?","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"Read more","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"The Times did not publish the email","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"- sent by Rob Goldstone , the intermediary","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"who set up the meeting -","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"but reported","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that three different people had described it to them .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Trump Jr ' s meeting is the first \" clear evidence \" in public of senior Trump campaign members","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"meeting with Russians","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"while looking for such material ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"a leading Democrat on the Senate intelligence committee said on Monday .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Mark Corallo , a spokesman for Marc Kasowitz , the president ' s private attorney","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"handling the Russia investigation ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"said simply :","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"\" The president was not aware of","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"and did not attend the meeting . \"","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"A spokeswoman for the DNC said :","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"\" Donald Jr was willing to accept the help of a hostile foreign government","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"to sway the election .","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"In the ensuing months , the Trump family watched","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"as news of the Kremlin ' s hacking campaign developed","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"and they did nothing","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"but celebrate","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"and encourage it to continue . \"","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"Alan Futerfas ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"appointed Trump Jr ' s lawyer","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"to represent him in the Russian investigations ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"described the New York Times report as \" much ado about nothing \" .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"In a statement","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"issued on Monday evening ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"Futerfas said","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"May and June 2016 had been \" an intensely busy time for Don Jr \" .","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"\" During this busy period , Robert Goldstone contacted Don Jr in an email","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"and suggested","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"that people had information","depth":16},{"id":43,"text":"concerning alleged wrongdoing by Democratic party front-runner , Hillary Clinton , in her dealings with Russia , \"","depth":16},{"id":44,"text":"the statement said .","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"\" Don Jr had no knowledge","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"as to what specific information ,","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"if any ,","depth":15},{"id":48,"text":"would be discussed . ...","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"The meeting lasted about 20-30 minutes ,","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"and nothing came of it .","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"His father knew nothing about it .","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"The bottom line is that Don , Jr. did nothing wrong . \"","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"Mark Warner of Virginia , the top Democrat on the intelligence committee , said","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"he \" absolutely \" wanted to speak to the president ' s son about the meeting . \"","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"This is the first time","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"that the public has seen clear evidence","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"of senior-level members of the Trump campaign meeting with Russians \"","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"to obtain information","depth":15},{"id":59,"text":"damaging to Clinton ,","depth":15},{"id":60,"text":"Warner said .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"Trump Jr attended the meeting in June 2016 at Trump Tower in New York","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"- allegedly brokered by Goldstone , a British music publicist -","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"with Veselnitskaya , a lawyer","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"who reportedly has ties to the Kremlin ;","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"Paul Manafort ,","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"who was the Trump campaign ' s chairman at the time ,","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"and Donald Trump ' s son-in-law , Jared Kushner .","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"The revelation ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"first reported by the New York Times ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"was the first public evidence","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"that members of the Trump campaign were willing to accept Russian assistance .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"Donald Trump Jr 's message to Russian operatives ?","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"I 'm open for business |","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Richard Wolffe","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Read more","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Susan Collins of Maine told reporters","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"that \" our intelligence committee needs to interview him and others","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"who attended the meeting \"","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"as part of its investigation into Russian interference in the presidential election .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Adam Schiff , the top Democrat on the House intelligence committee , has made a similar demand .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"At the White House press briefing on Monday , the spokeswoman Sarah Huckabee Sanders insisted","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"\" the only thing inappropriate \" about Trump Jr ' s meeting was \" the people","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"who leaked \" the details .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"She added","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"that she did not know of any other meetings between Trump Jr and Russian nationals","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"and that Donald Trump had only learned of the meeting \" in the last several days \" .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"Alleged collusion between the Trump campaign and Moscow is the subject of an investigation by a special counsel .","depth":5},{"id":88,"text":"The president ,","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"who met his Russian counterpart , Vladimir Putin , for the first time last week ,","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"has dismissed the claims as \" fake news \" .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"Trump Jr has come under particular scrutiny","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"as he appeared to offer shifting explanations for the meeting .","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"On Monday , the 39-year-old businessman tweeted sarcastically :","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"\" Obviously I ' m the first person on a campaign","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"to ever take a meeting","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"to hear info about an opponent ...","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"went nowhere","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"but had to listen \" .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"That appeared at odds with his first statement on Saturday","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"when he omitted any mention of Clinton ,","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"the discussion focused on a defunct programme","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"that had allowed American adoptions of Russian children .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Then , on Sunday ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"as the New York Times broke fresh details ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"Trump Jr admitted","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"that Veselnitskaya told him","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"\" she had information","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"that individuals","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"connected to Russia","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"were funding the Democratic National Committee","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"[ DNC ]","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"and supporting Ms Clinton \" .","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"He added :","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"\" No details or supporting information was provided or even offered .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"It quickly became clear that she had no meaningful information . \"","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"he concluded","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"that claims of information on Clinton had been a \" pretext \"","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"for setting up the meeting","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"to talk about adoptions ,","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"and that his father had been unaware of the meeting .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"On Monday , he posted on Twitter :","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"\" No inconsistency in statements ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"meeting ended up being primarily about adoptions .","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"In response to further Q ' s I simply provided more details . \"","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"Veselnitskaya is a Russian criminal defence lawyer","depth":4},{"id":128,"text":"who has had a number of clients with links to Russian government officials .","depth":4},{"id":129,"text":"Her highest-profile case was the defence of Denis Katsyv , a Russian businessman","depth":4},{"id":130,"text":"accused of laundering a portion of the proceeds from a $ 230m tax fraud","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"uncovered by the lawyer Sergei Magnitsky ,","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"who later died in jail .","depth":5},{"id":133,"text":"What does Robert Mueller 's team tell us about the Russia investigation ?","depth":3},{"id":134,"text":"Read more","depth":3},{"id":135,"text":"The US imposed sanctions on officials","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"considered complicit in Magnitsky ' s death ,","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"which caused so much anger in Moscow","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"that the Kremlin banned US adoptions of Russian children in response .","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"Veselnitskaya ' s defence of Katsyv also fed into other parts of a campaign","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"to discredit Magnitsky and Hermitage Capital , the investment fund","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"that had retained him .","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"She was involved in promoting a dubious film","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"that attacked Magnitsky ,","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"attempting to organise its showing in the European parliament ,","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"and securing a screening in Washington last June , shortly after the meeting at Trump Tower .","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"Veselnitskaya told NBC on Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"that she had no Kremlin ties","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"and only wanted to discuss US sanctions on Russian officials , not Clinton .","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"Goldstone , a British music publicist and former tabloid journalist , told the Associated Press","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"he had set up the meeting on behalf of a client","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"named Emin Agalarov ,","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"the son of a Moscow-based developer","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"who tried to partner with Trump in a hotel project .","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"Donald Trump appeared in a music video with Agalarov in 2013","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"that featured several Miss Universe contestants .","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"In November that year , Trump tweeted to Agalarov :","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"\" I had a great weekend with you and your family .","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"You have done a FANTASTIC job .","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"TRUMP TOWER-MOSCOW is next .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"EMIN was WOW ! \"","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"In March , Trump Jr told the New York Times","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"that he had never met Russians in a campaign capacity .","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"Other senior figures have repeatedly said","depth":5},{"id":164,"text":"there were no contacts between the campaign and Russians .","depth":5},{"id":165,"text":"On Monday , the White House vehemently denied","depth":6},{"id":166,"text":"that Trump Jr ' s meeting was improper .","depth":6},{"id":167,"text":"Kellyanne Conway insisted","depth":7},{"id":168,"text":"that \" there ' s no evidence of collusion \" between Trump Jr and Veselnitskaya .","depth":7},{"id":169,"text":"\" No information was received","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"that was meaningful or helpful","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"and no action was taken , \"","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"she said on ABC television ' s Good Morning America .","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"\" There was no follow-up whatsoever . \"","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"Putin ' s spokesman , Dmitry Peskov , said","depth":5},{"id":175,"text":"the Kremlin did not know Veselnitskaya","depth":6},{"id":176,"text":"and \" can not keep track \" of every Russian lawyer","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"who holds meetings in Russia or abroad .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":355,"left":310,"right":354,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":304,"right":309,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":264,"right":303,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":264,"left":253,"right":263,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":192,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":187,"right":191,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":183,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":182,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":0,"right":181,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":181,"left":179,"right":180,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":179,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pa